        <abstract>
            <p>Praise of CD. Acknowledges his indebtedness to CD for defining the subject of plant fecundation.</p>
            <p>Expecting CD’s work on the effects of cross-fertilisation.</p>
            <p>CD has put him in touch with George Bentham.</p>
        </abstract>
